{"ja471:0.1":"Jataka ","ja471:0.2":"Dvadasakanipata ","ja471:0.3":"Culakunalavagga ","ja471:0.4":"8. Mendakapanhajataka ","ja471:1.1":"“Yesam na kadaci bhutapubbam, ","ja471:1.2":"Sakhyam sattapadampimasmi loke; ","ja471:1.3":"Jata amitta duve sahaya, ","ja471:1.4":"Patisandhaya caranti kissa hetu”. ","ja471:2.1":"“Yadi me ajja patarasakale, ","ja471:2.2":"Panham na sakkuneyyatha vattumetam; ","ja471:2.3":"Rattha pabbajayissami vo sabbe, ","ja471:2.4":"Na hi mattho duppannajatikehi”. ","ja471:3.1":"“Mahajanasamagamamhi ghore, ","ja471:3.2":"Janakolahalasangamamhi jate; ","ja471:3.3":"Vikkhittamana anekacitta, ","ja471:3.4":"Panham na sakkunoma vattumetam. ","ja471:4.1":"Ekaggacittava ekameka, ","ja471:4.2":"Rahasi gata attham nicintayitva; ","ja471:4.3":"Paviveke sammasitvana dhira, ","ja471:4.4":"Atha vakkhanti janinda etamattham”. ","ja471:5.1":"“Uggaputtarajaputtiyanam, ","ja471:5.2":"Urabbhassa mamsam piyam manapam; ","ja471:5.3":"Na sunakhassa te adenti mamsam, ","ja471:5.4":"Atha mendassa sunena sakhyamassa”. ","ja471:6.1":"“Cammam vihananti elakassa, ","ja471:6.2":"Assapitthattharassukhassa hetu; ","ja471:6.3":"Na ca te sunakhassa attharanti, ","ja471:6.4":"Atha mendassa sunena sakhyamassa”. ","ja471:7.1":"“Avellitasingiko hi mendo, ","ja471:7.2":"Na ca sunakhassa visanakani atthi; ","ja471:7.3":"Tinabhakkho mamsabhojano ca, ","ja471:7.4":"Atha mendassa sunena sakhyamassa”. ","ja471:8.1":"“Tinamasi palasamasi mendo, ","ja471:8.2":"Na ca sunakho tinamasi no palasam; ","ja471:8.3":"Ganheyya suno sasam bilaram, ","ja471:8.4":"Atha mendassa sunena sakhyamassa”. ","ja471:9.1":"“Atthaddhapado catuppadassa, ","ja471:9.2":"Mendo atthanakho adissamano; ","ja471:9.3":"Chadiyamaharati ayam imassa, ","ja471:9.4":"Mamsam aharati ayam amussa. ","ja471:10.1":"Pasadavaragato videhasettho, ","ja471:10.2":"Vitiharam annamannabhojananam; ","ja471:10.3":"Addakkhi kira sakkhikam janindo, ","ja471:10.4":"Bubhukkassa punnammukhassa cetam”. ","ja471:11.1":"“Labha vata me anapparupa, ","ja471:11.2":"Yassa medisa pandita kulamhi; ","ja471:11.3":"Panhassa gambhiragatam nipunamattham, ","ja471:11.4":"Pativijjhanti subhasitena dhira. ","ja471:12.1":"Assatarirathanca ekamekam, ","ja471:12.2":"Phitam gamavaranca ekamekam; ","ja471:12.3":"Sabbesam vo dammi panditanam, ","ja471:12.4":"Paramappatitamano subhasitena”ti. ","ja471:13.1":"Mendakapanhajatakam atthamam. "}